import {Fragment} from 'react';
import Box from "@mui/material/Box";
import { AppBar } from '@mui/material';

function Home(){
    return(
        <Fragment>
            <Box sx={{ flexGrow: 1 }}>
                <AppBar position="static">
                    <Typography
                        variant="h6"
                        noWrap
                        component="div"
                        sx={{ flexGrow: 1, display: { xs: 'none', sm: 'block' } }}
                    >
                        MUI
                    </Typography>  
                </AppBar>
                
            </Box>


            <Box>
                Image
            </Box>
            <Box>
                Text Bar Input
            </Box>
            <Box>
                Enter Button
            </Box>
        </Fragment>
    )
}

export default Home;
